   618|/**
   619| * Run the pre-execution feasibility gate. Decomposes the prompt into required
   620| * capabilities, verifies each one against the real runtime, and returns either
   621| * READY (all checks pass) or BLOCKED with the exact blocker.
   622| *
   623| * The gate is the single source of truth for "can this actually be executed
   624| * right now?". It MUST run before any tool execution, patch, commit, deploy,
   625| * database migration, or proof claim.
